<subSubSection pageNumber="779" type="discussion">
<paragraph pageNumber="779">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="779">Note:</emphasis>
An illegitimate replacement name for the earlier 
<taxonomicName authority="Jacq." authorityName="Jacq." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Pterocarpus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="officinalis">
